org.ojai.annotation

Annotation Type API.NonNullable


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value={FIELD,PARAMETER,METHOD})
public static @interface API.NonNullable
    Annotate a class field, method parameter or return value as non-nullable, i.e. null is NOT an acceptable value for that parameter.

    A NullPointerException will be thrown if null is passed for such a parameter.

    See Also:
    API.Nullable
